info.name: Infamous: Second Son - Roblox
info.description: This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so describe the pic you want in the comments in detail or send an imgur link to it. If you find a better-quality image put an imgur link to it in the comments. Incredibly Low Quality Warning: The original image was meant as a phone wallpaper, making it a desktop wallpaper made it horribly blown up and lost a lot of the details that the original background had. The theme colours are pretty mediocre too, give suggestions on what other colour I should choose. Credits go to >Infamous: Second SonCode<, third in the series. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads, or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. A disclaimer: all the translations I make are just Google translated, I ain't no multilingual savant, so if there are any readers who are proficient in the languages above, please do tell me where I've messed up. 23 July 2023 - Released.
